description:
In this video we've put together a compilation of 7 Animated Bible stories for you to enjoy all in one go! So sit back and enjoy some of our most popular videos, and stay tuned because we're bringing LOTS more longer and better Bible stories to you soon! ❤️ ✝️

Don't forget to hit the SUBSCRIBE button, giving us a thumbs up, comment your thoughts below and share this video with your friends and family! Every like, share and comment helps us bring more videos your way! ❤️

► TIMESTAMPS:
00:00 - Noah's Ark 
03:45 - Sodom and Gomorrah
05:55 - Fall of Babylon
08:11 - Tower of Babel
10:59 - Moses and the 10 Commandments
13:32 - Battle of Jericho
15:17 - Jesus Escape From King Herod
